    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115020/extras/9cbd76dc322976bb91e696b939b385b4.webp?t=1707682321\" width=600 height=50 /></span><br><br>What if you could explore a world of endless possibilities where the only limit is your imagination? Welcome to Froggin Up, the thrilling ‘Tall Platformer’ game that will take you on an unforgettable adventure!<br><br>Take a leap of faith across the sprawling caverns, glide through the lush rainforests, climb the winding mountains, and soar among the stars!<br><br>Enjoy the story-driven experience as you jump, hop, and slide through different zones, discovering new areas and uncovering secrets. <br><br>No matter what direction you choose, you can be sure you have the skills to complete your mission! So get ready to Froggin Up!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115020/extras/a5e6071d50475c65fc8a33e51dfd197c.avif?t=1707682321\" width=135 height=128 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115020/extras/9b639a669d3b6f56bacce4cdf37e71b8.webp?t=1707682321\" width=20 height=23 /></span> Long Wondering Platformer.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115020/extras/9b639a669d3b6f56bacce4cdf37e71b8.webp?t=1707682321\" width=20 height=23 /></span> Continuous Saving Story.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115020/extras/9b639a669d3b6f56bacce4cdf37e71b8.webp?t=1707682321\" width=20 height=23 /></span> Rewind Time.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115020/extras/9b639a669d3b6f56bacce4cdf37e71b8.webp?t=1707682321\" width=20 height=23 /></span> Original Soundtrack.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115020/extras/9b639a669d3b6f56bacce4cdf37e71b8.webp?t=1707682321\" width=20 height=23 /></span> Narrator to Judge you along the way.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115020/extras/9b639a669d3b6f56bacce4cdf37e71b8.webp?t=1707682321\" width=20 height=23 /></span> Time Trials and new frogs!<br><br>We promise this will be the best cup of coffee you will ever buy!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115020/extras/c46f850eda07ec7be559a159b2952da9.webp?t=1707682321\" width=600 height=50 /></span>",
